    <item>
      <title>银行盈利强劲，推动股市突破 2023 年水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/banks-put-up-strong-earnings-pushing-stocks-beyond-2023-levels</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是一个漫长而艰难的攀登，但好于预期的财报季正在推动银行股回到 2023 年地区银行业危机之前的最高水平，表明投资者终于恢复了对金融业的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/banks-put-up-strong-earnings-pushing-stocks-beyond-2023-levels</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 16:06:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥商品交易所 (CME) 向耶伦求助，争夺美国国债主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/cme-turns-to-yellen-in-battle-for-dominance-of-us-treasuries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[芝加哥商品交易所集团 (CME Group Inc.) 正在加大对美国国债期货市场份额的争夺，全力阻止霍华德·鲁特尼克 (Howard Lutnick) 推出在伦敦清算的竞争合约的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/cme-turns-to-yellen-in-battle-for-dominance-of-us-treasuries</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 15:50:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>宝马因火灾隐患在华召回近 70 万辆汽车</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/bmw-recalls-almost-700-000-cars-in-china-on-fire-safety-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宝马汽车公司 (BMW AG) 因冷却泵缺陷在中国召回近 70 万辆汽车，这对于已深陷其他车辆故障泥潭的德国汽车制造商而言，无疑是雪上加霜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/bmw-recalls-almost-700-000-cars-in-china-on-fire-safety-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 14:50:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
