    <item>
      <title>中国经济提振抵消疲弱盈利影响，欧洲股市领涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/european-stocks-little-changed-as-earnings-misses-fan-jitters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管一些企业盈利报告表现平淡，但中国刺激市场的举措仍引发乐观情绪，推动欧洲股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-18/european-stocks-little-changed-as-earnings-misses-fan-jitters</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 18 Oct 2024 07:11:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
